original: Lagebrant, Sixten Manne, jur. kand., Norrköping, f. 12/12/19 i Stenstorp, Skarab. 1. G. 47 m. Inez Rosman. — x\vg:ex. fr. Norrköp. h. folksk. handelslinje 35, stud:ex. i Malmö 40, jur. kand. i Sthlm 44. Kont. o. sekr. h. adv. Axel Hemmar i Norrköp. 36-39, tingstjg. i Hall. mell. doms. samt Åse, Viste, Barne o. Laske doms. 44-46, bitr. jurist å Axel Hemmars Advrbyrå i Norrköp. sed. 46. Resor t. Danm. 36, Finl. 45.
translated: Lagebrant, Sixten Manne, LL.B., Norrköping, b. 12/12/19 in Stenstorp, Skaraborg. 1. M. 47 to Inez Rosman. - x/widow: former spouse of Norrköping higher elementary school trade line 35, student graduate in Malmö 40, LL.B. in Stockholm 44. Employed as a clerk and secretary for attorney Axel Hemmar in Norrköping from 36-39, served as a court clerk in the Halland intermediate court and Åse, Viste, Barne and Laske district courts from 44-46, assistant lawyer at Axel Hemmar's Law Firm in Norrköping since 46. Traveled to Denmark in 36 and Finland in 45.

employmentHistory.description: Served in the Halland intermediate court and Åse, Viste, Barne, and Laske district courts
